race.comment: ONE MORE CAKE (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 461m behind Aeroplane Bernie (27.04) in a Grade 4/5. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Has ability and is a key runner. SPICE LADY (7) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when second (30.18) at Launceston. Likely to be in the finish again. REIKO HULK (2) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at this track over 461m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Leading player again. THAT'S WHEN (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
